---
title: Creamy Garlic Chicken Pasta with Baby Spinach
description: The pasta dish loved by all is here in all its classic glory: a delicious garlicky cream sauce smothering juicy chicken breasts and penne, with baby spinach to get in those greens! You know the deal! Dive in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-au-poulet-et-sauce-cremeuse-a-lail-de7476a0.jpg
